description:
It was discovered that ROOT incorrectly handled certain input arguments. An
attacker could possibly use this issue to execute arbitrary code.

title: ROOT vulnerability
action: In general, a standard system update will make all the necessary changes.
isummary:
ROOT could be made to crash if it received specially crafted
input.
